@database "Example of accessing arexx commands from AmigaGuide"
@author   "Christer Bjarnemo"
@wordwrap
@index "INDEX"

@NODE MAIN

This is an example of how to use my arexx scripts use EMAIL, WWW and FTP
from AmigaGuide documents...

Send mail to me @{"mr.bjarnemo@mn.medstroms.se" system "run >CON: sys:rexxc/rx MAIL mr.bjarnemo@mn.medstroms.se"}
Access the @{"Amosaic 2.0 WWW page" system "run >CON: sys:rexxc/rx www http://www.omnipresence.com/amosaic/2.0/"}
Download @{"Amosaic 1.2" system "run >CON: sys:rexxc/rx ftpget ftp:ftp-uni-kl.de/pub/aminet/comm/tcp/Mosaic1.2AmiTC.lha"} from Aminet.
Download @{"FTPMount" system "run >CON: sys:rexxc/rx ftpget ftp:ftp-uni-kl.de/pub/aminet/comm/tcp/FTPMount.lha"} from Aminet.
Download @{"Amiga Elm" system "run >CON: sys:rexxc/rx ftpget ftp:ftp-uni-kl.de/pub/aminet/comm/mail/AmigaElm-v8.lha} from Aminet.
         @{"Send a file" system "run >CON: sys:rexxc/rx ftpput"} to a ftp site.

@ENDNODE
